description: Everything about Mama Kim's is local. Awesome young chefs from Johnson & Wales cook our food the way it's supposed to be cooked. Our logo and truck design were made by RISD students. Brown Professors advise our enterprise. We have formed a strong partnership with local suppliers so that we can deliver amazingly fresh food at affordable prices. It's mom's great cooking, meet Rhode Island pride!
name: Mama Kim's Korean BBQ
